dc_title_s: Le plan de Paris, ses Faubourgs et ses environs; par Guillaume de L'Isle = Platte grond van Parys, zyn voorburgen en omleggende plaatse.; Platte grond van Parys, zyn voorburgen en omleggende plaatse
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Originally published in Paris in 1716. Shows selected named buildings (some in perspective), gardens, fields. The coloring is original or early hand color. 1 map: col.; 61 x 80 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
